LOCUS       pT7L0_mScarlet_pTI      5901 bp ds-DNA     circular     03-DEC-2024
DEFINITION  .
COMMENT     mScarlet-I expression under pT7_Lac0 promoter (i.e. It has a Lac0
            box to improve the promoter repression).  This system drives the
            expression of mScarlet-I in the presence of RNAT7 polymerase (which
            typically is induced by IPTG in E.coli BL21).
            pT7_Lac0::Riboj54_B0034::His_tag::GS_linker::mScarlet::3xStop::Tz
            in pTI mScarlet-I is a Red-Orange fluorescent protein Kanamycin
            Resistant pBR322 ORI + ROP (low-middle copy) LacI translation rate
            from 4valine : 2275.31 accord to RBS calculator.
